<P>
May 25, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Life & Style; Part E; Page 2; Column 2; View Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
18 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
EDITOR'S NOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Doonesbury is fanciful satire. Truth is, the individuals named in this comic 
strip have not been indicted. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA052594-0019 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 044941 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 25, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
