"Schindler's List." 
</P>
<P>
 James Kirby pleaded guilty to assault Monday in connection with the Jan. 6 
shooting of Ellen Campbell as she sat in front of him at a downtown theater. 
</P>
<P>
 "I think he should go to prison," said Campbell, who is recuperating from the 
