Calif. 6. Virginia Beach, Va. 7. Sterling Heights, Mich. 8. Madison, Wis. 9. 
Scottsdale, Ariz. 10. Thousand Oaks 11. Rancho Cucamonga 12. Plano, Tex. 13. 
Salem, Ore. 14. Arlington, Va. 15. Glendale 
