<TEXT>
<P>
 Name: Gheorghe Hagi. 
</P>
<P>
 Born: Feb. 5, 1965, Sacele, Romania. 
</P>
<P>
 Height: 5-8. 
</P>
<P>
 Weight: 156 pounds. 
</P>
<P>
 Position: Midfielder. 
</P>
<P>
 Club: Brescia (Serie B, Italy). 
</P>
<P>
 National team debut: 1983, vs. Norway. 
</P>
<P>
 Caps (international matches): 81. 
</P>
<P>
